-- Carlyle Is Considering Making Offer for Gruppo Coin, De Benedetti Says
-- B y   E l i s a   M a r t i n u z z i
-- 2010-10-05T12:05:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/carlyle-is-considering-making-offer-for-gruppo-coin-de-benedetti-says.html
The Carlyle Group is considering
making a bid for Gruppo Coin, said Marco De Benedetti, head of
Washington-based Carlyle’s private equity business in Italy.  Coin will draw “ a lot of interest,” De Benedetti told
reporters in Milan. The private-equity firm has already started
working on the bid, he added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisa Martinuzzi in Milan at 
 emartinuzzi@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
